        <Parent_String>Persian pottery styles [300107783], Persian styles [300020041], Persian (culture) [300019933], Near Eastern (Early Western World) [300019571], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
